    },
    {
      "text": "Super Keirin (スーパー競輪, Super Keirin) is a Japanese-exclusive video game with gambling/life sim elements, where players take control of their character and make money by betting on cycle races at the local Velodrome.\nCute anime-style graphics are employed throughout the game; stating that the premise of the game is less serious than other Super NES gambling style video games.",
